            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社10日專訊》中國人大會議閉幕,及日本公布第四季GDP,料為周二(11日)市場焦點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　各國重要經濟活動方面,中國十四屆全國人大三次會議閉幕。歐洲經濟暨財政事務理事會會議舉行,歐洲央行副總裁德金多斯與會。周二本港時間5:00pm,芬蘭央行總裁暨歐洲央行管委雷恩談論芬蘭和<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/eurusd\">歐元</a>區經濟的貨幣政策和前景。</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">*澳洲公布NAB企業信心指數,日本公布工具機訂單*</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　數據方面,周二(11日)7:50am(本港時間.下同),日本公布第四季國內生產總值,經季節調整季率升幅料由0.3%擴大至0.7%;2月貨幣供應M2;2月貨幣供應M3</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">。8:30am,澳洲公布2月NAB企業信心指數。2:00pm,日本公布2月工具機訂單。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　在本港,明日公布業績的公司有:陽光房地產基金(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00435:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00435\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00435-HK</a>)、裕元集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00551:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00551\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00551-HK</a>)、鷹普精密(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01286:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01286\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01286-HK</a>)、金斯瑞生物科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01548:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01548\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01548-HK</a>)、東曜藥業-B(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01875:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01875\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01875-HK</a>)、BOSS直聘-W(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02076:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02076\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02076-HK</a>)、TOM集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02383:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02383\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02383-HK</a>)、德康農牧(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02419:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02419\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02419-HK</a>)、寶勝國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03813:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03813\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03813-HK</a>)等。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　另外,美國周三(12日)公布2月消費物價指數(CPI),周四(13日)公布2月生產物價指數(PPI)。(wa)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
